headline: Gary Godin and Sean McCartney Appointed to Jointly Lead Pacific Life’s Workforce Benefits Business
summary: NEWPORT BEACH, Calif., August 28, 2025--Pacific Life has promoted Gary Godin and Sean McCartney to senior vice presidents to jointly lead its Workforce Benefits business.
